Tags.string 'NodeComment': Using a timeline and an angle specified by the level designer to rotate the ramp up or down.
The ramp can be triggered and is rotated so it can open new paths in the level. This is very limited behaviour but you could extend or even build a whole bridge with several ones in a similar way.

Like the door and other game objects, the ramp can reqyire more than one trigger. You can specify an array of triggers and how many are required to be active, which makes it quite flexible. For more details check out the BP_Door.
